{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/sebastianbergmann/phpunit/issues/413","repository_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/sebastianbergmann/phpunit","labels_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/sebastianbergmann/phpunit/issues/413/labels{/name}","comments_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/sebastianbergmann/phpunit/issues/413/comments","events_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/sebastianbergmann/phpunit/issues/413/events","html_url":"https://github.com/sebastianbergmann/phpunit/issues/413","id":2269698,"node_id":"MDU6SXNzdWUyMjY5Njk4","number":413,"title":".phpt test failures display double diffs","user":{"login":"joncave","id":621103,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjYyMTEwMw==","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/621103?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/joncave","html_url":"https://github.com/joncave","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/joncave/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/joncave/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/joncave/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/joncave/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/joncave/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/joncave/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/joncave/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/joncave/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/joncave/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false},"labels":[],"state":"closed","locked":false,"assignee":null,"assignees":[],"milestone":null,"comments":0,"created_at":"2011-11-17T15:09:52Z","updated_at":"2011-11-25T13:48:42Z","closed_at":"2011-11-25T13:48:42Z","author_association":"CONTRIBUTOR","active_lock_reason":null,"sub_issues_summary":{"total":0,"completed":0,"percent_completed":0},"issue_dependencies_summary":{"blocked_by":0,"total_blocked_by":0,"blocking":0,"total_blocking":0},"body":"When a .phpt test is run through phpunit and fails it displays Expected/Actual difference twice.\n\nExample test.phpt:\n\n```\n--TEST--\nvar_dump boolean\n--FILE--\n<?php\nvar_dump(false);\n--EXPECT--\nbool(true)\n```\n\nOutput:\n\n```\n$ phpunit test.phpt \nPHPUnit 3.6.3 by Sebastian Bergmann.\n\nF\n\nTime: 0 seconds, Memory: 6.50Mb\n\nThere was 1 failure:\n\n1) test.phpt\n--- Expected\n+++ Actual\n@@ @@\n-bool(true)\n+bool(false)\n\n--- Expected\n+++ Actual\n@@ @@\n-bool(true)\n+bool(false)\n\n\nFAILURES!\nTests: 1, Assertions: 1, Failures: 1.\n```\n\nExtract from PHPUnit_Framework_TestFailure::exceptionToString():\n\n``` php\n$buffer = $e->toString();\n\nif ($e instanceof PHPUnit_Framework_ComparisonFailure) {\n     $buffer = trim($buffer . \"\\n\" . $e->getDiff());\n}\n```\n\nPHPUnit_Framework_ComparisonFailure already includes the output from getDiff() in toString() so it is doubled up.\n\nRelated commits 452f50a86c9c96f1920945b875b756c184080b21 and 7b37221b785dd5aeda8794e8ffdcbfd8cf3aad7b.\n","closed_by":{"login":"edorian","id":247397,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjI0NzM5Nw==","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/247397?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/edorian","html_url":"https://github.com/edorian","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/edorian/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/edorian/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/edorian/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/edorian/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/edorian/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/edorian/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/edorian/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/edorian/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/edorian/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false},"reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/sebastianbergmann/phpunit/issu